  <brief_title>Contact Force Sensing Use in Atrial Fibrillation Ablation</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Contact Force Sensing in Electrical Pulmonary Vein Isolation When Conducting Atrial Fibrillation Ablation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Royal Brompton &amp; Harefield NHS Foundation Trust</agency>
